## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/orc/executorprocesscontrol">ExecutorProcessControl</a> supports interaction with a JIT target process.

Run a wrapper function using SPS to serialize the arguments and deserialize the results.

### callWrapper() {#a1140ddd9e676afc51207f47d6730acf9}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>shared::WrapperFunctionResult llvm::orc::ExecutorProcessControl::callWrapper (<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/orc/executoraddr">ExecutorAddr</a> WrapperFnAddr, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/arrayref">ArrayRef</a>&lt; char &gt; ArgBuffer)</>}
  labels = {["inline"]}>
Run a wrapper function in the executor.
